acceptance_criteria: "ADR drafted and driven to accepted/rejected: enumerates GA criteria (frozen ~15-noun grammar per pm-pbyu, semver-stable SDK primitive surface per pm-muhw, storage format_version compatibility guarantees, scripting contract pm-psy1 as a tested guarantee, scale targets from pm-9rxu benchmarks) and the deprecation policy that carries pre-1.0 spellings; linked from milestone pm-doxj as horizon 4"
